properties.areaDesc: Los Angeles County Coast including Downtown Los Angeles
properties.headline: Wind Advisory issued January 28 at 8:47PM PST until January 30 at 10:00AM PST by NWS Los Angeles/Oxnard CA
properties.description:
* WHAT...North winds 15 to 25 mph with gusts up to 40 mph.

* WHERE...Los Angeles County Coast, from the Hollywood Hills to
Malibu.

* WHEN...Until 10 AM PST Thursday.

* IMPACTS...Damaging winds could blow down large objects such as
trees and power lines. Power outages are possible. Travel could
be difficult, especially for high profile vehicles.
properties.instruction:
Use extra caution when driving, especially if operating a high
profile vehicle. Secure outdoor objects.

NWSheadline: WIND ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 10 AM PST THURSDAY
